text: in Baghdad Iraqi security forces
celebrated the American troops
withdrawal from city centers with songs
and colored ribbons we hope that the
American forces and the other forces in
Iraq will leave to grant Iraq
independence and unity but while some
celebrated on the streets others were
more skeptical this is not a full
withdrawal the Americans are staying God
willing the streets of Iraq will be
empty of American forces God willing
there will be more freedom
the Iraqi people learned about fear by
living it they do not trust the Iraqi
army and police forces it is true that
the army was weak but it gained
expertise from the American forces I
think they are capable now I think the
presence of American forces in the
desert is good for you wrap the
